</header><div class="entry-content" itemprop="text"><p><a title="Sandersons Boday Repairs" href="http://www.sandersonsbodyrepairs.com.au/">Sandersons Body Repairs</a> is a family owned and operated business established on the Gold Coast and conveniently located on Brisbane Road, at Labrador.  We pride ourselves on excellent service and guaranteed quality smash repairs from our team of <a href="http://www.sandersonsbodyrepairs.com.au/about/">qualified tradesmen.</a></p>
<div id="attachment_83" style="width: 710px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img class="size-full wp-image-83" src="http://www.sandersonsbodyrepairs.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/paul-desk.jpg" alt="Friendly Expert Service Guaranteed" width="700" height="297" srcset="http://www.sandersonsbodyrepairs.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/paul-desk.jpg 700w, http://www.sandersonsbodyrepairs.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/paul-desk-300x127.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" /><p class="wp-caption-text">Friendly Expert Service Guaranteed</p></div>
<p>At <a href="http://www.sandersonsbodyrepairs.com.au/">Sandersons Prestige Accident Repair</a> Centre we boast the latest and greatest equipment used to ensure high quality, undetectable repairs, and friendly, professional staff who will put you at ease while they care for your car.</p>
<h2>Smash Repairs Gold Coast</h2>
<p>We are experts in the full range of <a title="smash repairs gold coast" href="http://www.sandersonsbodyrepairs.com.au/">smash repairs Gold Coast</a> and boast a convenient central location.  We would be so delighted to assist you in getting your car repaired and back on the road.</p>
<blockquote><p><em>Paul takes care of everything, takes good care of your precious car and delivers the best service with a smile. Highly recommended for small dents and paint repairs, accident repairs and repaints. Really fast, quality repair work to make your car look better than ever.</em></p>
<p><em><strong>Edgar.</strong></em></p>
<h4>SANDERSONS, <em>quality and service guaranteed&#8230;</em></h4>
</blockquote>
